357
00:16:32,364 --> 00:16:33,514
à l'autre.

358
00:17:28,496 --> 00:17:29,842
Je me rappelle de vous.

359
00:17:31,706 --> 00:17:32,951
On va dans l'eau ?

360
00:17:33,805 --> 00:17:34,805
Carrément !

361
00:17:48,039 --> 00:17:49,987
À quelle heure le mariage commence ?

362
00:17:50,475 --> 00:17:51,676
La classique, Bob.

363
00:17:55,593 --> 00:17:57,120
Tout ce que je fais...

